OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779282675
OL,3,CBodies of two more scuba divers
OL,4,Crecovered from underwater cave in
OL,5,CMaldives
OL,7,FDivers have recovered the last two
OL,8,Fbodies of the five Italians who died
OL,9,Fdeep inside an underwater cave in the
OL,10,FMaldives last week.
OL,12,FThe Italian divers had been exploring
OL,13,Fthe cave in Vaavu Atoll last Thursday
OL,14,Fwhen they disappeared.
OL,16,FThe body of their Italian diving
OL,17,Finstructor was recovered outside the
OL,18,Fcave last week, and the Finnish
OL,19,Frecovery divers brought the bodies of
OL,20,Ftwo of the divers to the surface on
OL,21,FTuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
