FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779282675
OL,3,CBodies of two more scuba divers
OL,4,Crecovered from underwater cave in
OL,5,CMaldives
OL,7,FPresidential spokesperson Mohameed
OL,8,FHussain Shareef said the last two
OL,9,Fbodies were recovered by three Finnish
OL,10,Fdivers supported by the Maldives
OL,11,Fcoastguard and police.
OL,13,FHe said they would be taken to a
OL,14,Fmorgue to be identified.
OL,16,F"After that, we will coordinate with
OL,17,Fthe Italian government and start the
OL,18,Fprocedure to repatriate the bodies,"
OL,19,Fhe said. He thanked the Finnish
OL,20,Fdivers, praising them for their
OL,21,Fprofessionalism and leadership.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
