CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779282675
OL,3,CBodies of two more scuba divers
OL,4,Crecovered from underwater cave in
OL,5,CMaldives
OL,7,FThe bodies had been located Monday at
OL,8,Fa depth of around 60 meters (200
OL,9,Ffeet), twice the legal depth for
OL,10,Frecreational diving in the island
OL,11,Fnation.
OL,13,FThe search had been temporarily
OL,14,Fsuspended after a local military diver
OL,15,Fdied during a perilous retrieval
OL,16,Fattempt.
OL,18,FThe Maldives government said the
OL,19,Frecovery divers spotted the bodies in
OL,20,Fthe cave's innermost area.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779282675
OL,3,CBodies of two more scuba divers
OL,4,Crecovered from underwater cave in
OL,5,CMaldives
OL,7,FGovernment spokesperson Ahmed Shaam
OL,8,Fsaid the four bodies were found
OL,9,F"pretty much together".
OL,11,FThe cave has been explored in the past
OL,12,Fby local experts and foreign divers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
