OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779282675
OL,3,CBodies of two more scuba divers
OL,4,Crecovered from underwater cave in
OL,5,CMaldives
OL,7,FWhile the Italian divers had a permit,
OL,8,Fauthorities didn't know from their
OL,9,Fproposal the exact location of the
OL,10,Fcave they were exploring, and at least
OL,11,Ftwo of the dead were not on the list
OL,12,Fof researchers that had been
OL,13,Fsubmitted, "so we didn't know they
OL,14,Fwere part of the expedition," Shareef
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
