OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779282675
OL,3,CBodies of two more scuba divers
OL,4,Crecovered from underwater cave in
OL,5,CMaldives
OL,7,FHe described the conditions deep in
OL,8,Fthe cave as "challenging" with
OL,9,Fdifficult terrain, strong currents and
OL,10,Fpoor visibility.
OL,12,FHe said an alert had also been issued
OL,13,Fdue to bad weather, and investigators
OL,14,Fmust determine whether the divers took
OL,15,Fadequate precautions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
