CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779282675
OL,3,CBodies of two more scuba divers
OL,4,Crecovered from underwater cave in
OL,5,CMaldives
OL,7,FThe rescue team used closed-circuit
OL,8,Frebreathers, a system that recycles
OL,9,Fexhaled breathing gas and removes
OL,10,Fcarbon dioxide through a chemical
OL,11,Fscrubber, allowing for "significantly
OL,12,Flonger dives," the organisation said.
OL,14,FThe cause of death of the Maldivian
OL,15,Fmilitary diver was still under
OL,16,Finvestigation, but colleagues have
OL,17,Fsuggested he may have died from
OL,18,Fnitrogen narcosis or decompression at
OL,19,Fdepth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
